Semifinals [Mar 14/15, Mar 21]
La Serena    0-3 2-2 U. de Chile
Temuco       0-0 0-2 A. Italiano

Final [Mar 28, Apr 1]
U. de Chile  1-1 2-0 A. Italiano

Universidad de Chile winners Copa Chile 1998; in principle this
qualifies them for the Copa Conmebol 1998, but since U. de Chile
will play in the Copa Mercosur 1998, Audax Italiano take their
place in the Copa Conmebol instead.
